overview: Tushy knows there's happy, there's ecstatic, and there's Anal Bliss. This series takes a deep dive into backdoor euphoria. Featured cover girl Savannah Bond is married to a power player under intense pressure. He might be the breadwinner, but this bootylicious blonde makes the rules, and she's not letting him leave until they've both blown off some steam. Kagney Linn Karter, Lara Frost, and Clea Gaultier are all supplying rapturous sexual energy.
title: Anal Bliss 2
